metadata.name: "Rain"
metadata.description:
"That feeling of loneliness, when everything around you feels heavy, sometimes you just want let it all out. Like the rain, it seems so endless, pouring a never ending emotion of sorrow and pain. But like any other thing in life, this too shall pass.."
